{"tid":139594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實拍拖有咩可以做","createTime":"2017-03-01T14:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T20:04:00.000Z","uid":41953,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c56eb1cfb9a665eb40b86a352f758cc3c9f8c2e1","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"黎黎去去都係果啲<br />\n自己份人本身都悶 男朋友又係果啲冇乜情趣嘅人<br />\n就黎大家都俾大家悶死<br />\n情人節好似平時咁過，同埋唔洗旨意佢會做啲咩浪漫野<br />\n沙灘用蠟燭砌心心果啲我諗我一世都冇可能見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時送禮物都冇驚喜，因為我一定會估到or佢話我知係咩<br />\n而且都少送<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時淨係喺屋企訓教，睇下電影咁"},{"pid":"5ff90fd75678d238b106c6292b0e5676a1a53794","tid":139594,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"你中意佢啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似係為拍而拍多"},{"pid":"f9a8457230f991ed50743967700c88dc3a162ed3","tid":139594,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79ca5cbf8784dc1890864b9c8a075e42e0ebf96","tid":139594,"uid":14932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"見到佢咪得 做啲咩都開心啦<br />\n你都諗唔到想做咩佢又唔介意又有咩所謂"},{"pid":"cc2b66207cfe3b06adaebc4ee2a378050a589ee9","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你中意佢啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似係為拍而拍多</blockquote><br />\n佢對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前同佢一齊覺得佢係一個好有自己想法嘅人好聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋啱啱一齊果陣普通行下街都覺得好開心好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1c0ab0a8a123ee2230de5526fd30f56ee4f8cd","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到佢咪得 做啲咩都開心啦<br />\n你都諗唔到想做咩佢又唔介意又有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n佢成日嫌我冇興趣,唔鍾意睇漫畫唔鍾意打機唔鍾意睇戲<br />\n我又嫌佢悶黎黎去去都係呢啲"},{"pid":"d92b54fb6e61ecbf126dbb2f6cb2d9e5b49ac521","tid":139594,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"愛❤️"},{"pid":"397044ceac0b9615bad0c34452ed9b1b35cb6080","tid":139594,"uid":62260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎黎去去都係果啲<br />\n自己份人本身都悶 男朋友又係果啲<span style=\"color: red;\">冇乜情趣</span>嘅人<br />\n就黎大家都俾大家悶死<br />\n情人節好似平時咁過，同埋唔洗旨意佢會做啲咩浪漫野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沙灘用蠟燭砌心心果啲我諗我一世都冇可能見到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時<span style=\"color: red;\">送禮物都冇驚喜</span>，因為我一定會估到or<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話我知係咩</span><br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">都少送</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時淨係喺屋企訓教，<span style=\"color: red;\">睇下電影</span>咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2"},{"pid":"60d95947c9ee576bf1d9ffeddf3723cbbb96364a","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎黎去去都係果啲<br />\n自己份人本身都悶 男朋友又係果啲<span style=\"color: red;\">冇乜情趣</span>嘅人<br />\n就黎大家都俾大家悶死<br />\n情人節好似平時咁過，同埋唔洗旨意佢會做啲咩浪漫野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沙灘用蠟燭砌心心果啲我諗我一世都冇可能見到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時<span style=\"color: red;\">送禮物都冇驚喜</span>，因為我一定會估到or<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話我知係咩</span><br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">都少送</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時淨係喺屋企訓教，<span style=\"color: red;\">睇下電影</span>咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d935aaf8788bbe2d5deac53e10bd25b61eaf6f4e","tid":139594,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"出軌會唔會刺激d 冇咁悶?"},{"pid":"ce146b939b1de0e72ae4681ef489e29a0d515fa9","tid":139594,"uid":14004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"拍拖就係將平時一個做嘅<br />\n變成兩個人一齊做。"},{"pid":"11a8094350d81ff9902b6de569b841d13bd461af","tid":139594,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖就係將平時一個做嘅<br />\n變成兩個人一齊做。</blockquote><br />\n又唔見份工啲野幫手做埋<br />\n3個人既工作量1個人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4d19d8ea769d36000d7ead38b2f8dfa47186a6","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出軌會唔會刺激d 冇咁悶?</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13baac1878bda7578538ec1d4a08430515a2ecd4","tid":139594,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3101303c6d9bba13a517843f95e4f93f91523ca6","tid":139594,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"咁佢果陣點追你"},{"pid":"4790d77b7c6c2d362100c614c1b4c5e821c0ca8a","tid":139594,"uid":72531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"做愛做的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c82063ecf611e7a97493aabcb7ebe3483c03a9f","tid":139594,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:47:28.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n我見到佢就已經好開心<br />\n有一個明我諗乜既人已經好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲洗乜做咩"},{"pid":"79ca8bceae435e298a2043bf0578c57673532daf","tid":139594,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:49:10.000Z","msg":"分手啦，佢都唔岩你，<br />\n你亦都唔係好鐘意佢"},{"pid":"9543e4dab2f30c0abfbd467881c9010a1b2bb344","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢果陣點追你</blockquote><br />\n果陣覺得佢講啲野好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但拍左拖之後冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a92b35f05103768717689bcfcf651147d5ef86","tid":139594,"uid":35888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下<br />\n我見到佢就已經好開心<br />\n有一個明我諗乜既人已經好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲洗乜做咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係咁諗"},{"pid":"aeccd0243e3a65bd55b1f51959145ce6477d5741","tid":139594,"uid":62859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"樓主好似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平淡同悶都唔係問題<br />\n係有時心諗兩個人咁樣唔似拍拖<br />\n同埋覺得另一半唔係好鐘意自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4854b65ecec756b73acee5fbd8fdfc7f045a7c3b","tid":139594,"uid":88503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手啦，佢都唔岩你，<br />\n你亦都唔係好鐘意佢</blockquote><br />\n同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同男朋友都係行下街睇戲食飯<br />\n情人節大家都要返工 前年仲各自返屋企訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但平平淡淡咁就已經好開心<br />\n得閒研究下有無手機game好玩<br />\n有時佢打機我就睇youtube<br />\n浪漫有浪漫好 平淡有平淡既溫馨<br />\n<br />\n利申 絲"},{"pid":"d54bdb5f95191f486a79317e46be6f5594bc679e","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平淡同悶都唔係問題<br />\n係有時心諗兩個人咁樣唔似拍拖<br />\n同埋覺得另一半唔係好鐘意自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我知道佢好鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd83f0c5343e9aeaca6e560d73bbe335deb8ec2d","tid":139594,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分手啦，佢都唔岩你，<br />\n你亦都唔係好鐘意佢</blockquote><br />\n同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同男朋友都係行下街睇戲食飯<br />\n情人節大家都要返工 前年仲各自返屋企訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但平平淡淡咁就已經好開心<br />\n得閒研究下有無手機game好玩<br />\n有時佢打機我就睇youtube<br />\n浪漫有浪漫好 平淡有平淡既溫馨<br />\n<br />\n利申 絲</blockquote><br />\n佢成日想我陪佢打機，我有努力嘗試過但真係唔特別想玩唔會驅使我主動同佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好鍾意做果啲野佢又嫌冇營養悶唔肯陪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後兩個坐埋一齊冇野做就訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca526e3ec1d88d5e980cab582c16ebd53824e7f","tid":139594,"uid":88230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}